      "The new Sky family of devices introduces solutions that address a broad range of clinical challenges, including Left Bundle Branch Area Pacing (LBBAP). It features a new anti-tachycardia pacing (ATP) suite to expand atrial and ventricular ATP options, and continues to offer BIOTRONIK\u2019s unique DX Technology, the only single-lead solution providing true atrial sensing without an additional atrial lead.",
      "BIOTRONIK at HRS 2026 BIOTRONIK will participate at the Heart Rhythm Society (HRS) congress taking place in Chicago, Illinois. Join us for interactive sessions, lectures, hands-on experiences and networking with the BIOTRONIK professionals."
